Preinstall
--------
p4


Run
--------
$ ./compile_bmv2.sh
$ ./network.py
$ ./send_cmd.sh

mininet> xterm h1 h2

(h1)$ ./sender.py
(h2)$ ./receiver.py


Curent method
--------
Proxy(only from proxy to router)
* Add token between IP header and TCP header
* Traffic monitor(count min sketch with 3 hashes)
	** IP 3 tuple as key
	** Constant threshold for heavy hitter detection
	** Timestamp window to exclude too old counts

Router
*Check token
	** drop packet if invalid
	
Support bi-direction

Current topology
--------
         h3 0 -- 1 s3 2
                      |
                      | 
h1 0 -- 1 P4s1 2 ---- R ---- 2 P4s2 1 ---- 0 h2
[     proxy    ]               [router]    [server]

Test
--------
Connectivity
1.	mininet> h1 ping h2
2.	h2> nc -l 1234
	h1> nc 10.2.0.100 1234 -p 5678
	h3> nc 10.2.0.100 1234 -p 5678

